description: 1101 W Sligh Ave, Tampa, FL 33604. Tel: 813-935-9552.  The zoo is on 56 acres and includes many animal encounters.  Park zones are dedicated to Asia, Africa, Australia, and Florida.  More than 1,300 separate animals call it home.
